ygData.messageBody:
I was kind of wondering why people downplayed Warsong, but wasn;t going
to say anything. I use it all the time, but then again I solo a lot
still (I have a good but small guild, so when they aren't around, I
usually solo, as pickup groups usually means lose xp for me).

BTW I hit (drumroll please...) lvl 20 this weekend! I was pretty damn
excited. Still working on that surname.

Elfson Allegro is my favorite so far...
--
We now return to the non-stop rock.

Matt DeBarger
